BRANDT-Claire (nee Grabois) on March 30th, 1999 at the age of 89. Beloved wife of the late Bernard. Loving mother of Neil and Susan and Lawrence and Lois. Cherished grandmother of Michael and Minna, Richard, Heather, Brooke and Gary Fishkind, and Michelle. Proud great-grandmother of Zachary Brandt Fishkind. Funeral service Friday, 9 AM, at Riverside Memorial Chapel, 21 West Broad Street, Mount Vernon, New York. Contributions may be made in her memory to the Juvenile Diabetes Foundation.